4. cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture) - The paper deals with communication channels, which is a key aspect of networking and internet architecture. 
5. cs.LG (Machine Learning) - Although not the main focus of the paper, the use of dirty paper codes is a technique that has been applied in machine learning for interference mitigation.
